            "title": "港股開市︱初段偏軟 恒指再跌28點報24744點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段偏軟，恒生指數開市報24744點，跌28點或0.12%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5447點，跌5點或0.09%；國企指數以8870點開市，跌12點或0.14%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股個別發展，阿里巴巴(09988)開報117.8元，升1.82%；騰訊(00700)開報551.5元，升0.27%；美團(03690)開報121.1元，跌0.41%；小米(01810)開報52.8元，跌0.66%。滙控(00005)開報95.5元，跌0.68%；友邦(01299)開報73.4元，暫時無升跌。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">小鵬汽車(09868)上月交付量按年大升2.29倍，再創新高；該股今早開報71.85元，升0.35%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小鵬汽車官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230818_FI_source-web_09868_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小鵬汽車官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230818_FI_source-web_09868_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小鵬汽車官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國儒意(00136)折讓4.46%配股籌39億元，該股今早開報3.1元，跌1.27%；開拓醫藥(09939)折讓近19%配股，該股今早開報2.55元，跌0.39%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大悅城地產(00207)以溢價67.57%回購並擬撤銷上市地位，該股今早復牌應聲彈升，開報0.55元，飆48.65%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15139070-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%81%8f%e8%bb%9f-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%86%8d%e8%b7%8c28%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b124744%e9%bb%9e",
