            "title": "開拓藥業折讓18.75%配股籌4300萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">開拓藥業(09939)公布，擬透過先舊後新方式配股集資約4300萬元；配股價2.08元，較該股昨收市價2.56元折讓約18.75%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以該股前5個交易日平均收市價2.558元計，配股價折讓18.69%，較前10個交易日平均收市價2.515元則折讓約17.3%。集資淨額約4034萬元，將用於一般營運資金及一般業務。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15139000-%e9%96%8b%e6%8b%93%e8%97%a5%e6%a5%ad%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%9318-75%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c4300%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/09939-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-01 08:45:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國儒意折讓4.46%配股籌39億元 主要用於戰略投資及收購",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國儒意(00136)今早公布，計畫配股集資約39億元；配股價3元，較該股昨天收市價3.14元折讓4.46%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國儒意官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250114_FI_source-web_00136.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國儒意官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250114_FI_source-web_00136.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國儒意官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以該股前5個交易日平均收市價3.23元計，配股價折讓約7.18%，較前10個交易日平均收市價3.27元則折讓約8.37%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">配售股份相等於該公司已擴大後股本約7.51%。集資淨額約38.95億元，約60%用於戰略性投資及收購，以擴大公司業務；約20%用於公司業務的增長及擴張；約20%用作一般營運資本用途。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15138990-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%84%92%e6%84%8f%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%934-46%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c39%e5%84%84%e5%85%83-%e4%b8%bb%e8%a6%81%e7%94%a8%e6%96%bc%e6%88%b0%e7%95%a5%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87%e5%8f%8a%e6%94%b6",
