        {
            "title": "小鵬汽車上月交付量按年增2.29倍創新高 首7月升2.7倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">小鵬汽車(09868)公布，今年7月份智能車交付刷新紀錄，達3.67萬輛，按年升2.29倍，也是連續9個月交付超過3萬輛。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小鵬汽車官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250612_FI_source-web_09868-G7-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小鵬汽車官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250612_FI_source-web_09868-G7-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小鵬汽車官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今年首7個月合計，交付智能電動汽車總數23.39萬輛，按增2.7倍；截至7月底，小鵬汽車累計總交付量超過80萬輛。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15138974-%e5%b0%8f%e9%b5%ac%e6%b1%bd%e8%bb%8a%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e4%ba%a4%e4%bb%98%e9%87%8f%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%a2%9e2-29%e5%80%8d%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98-%e9%a6%967%e6%9c%88%e5%8d%872-7%e5%80%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250311_FI_source-web_09868.jpg.webp",
